				</p>
			</div>
		</li>
		<li class="stack-trace top-left">
			<div class="bubble">
				<p>
					<strong>Navigable stack traces</strong>, mapped to your original source code, let you easily find what led up to the breaking code. <a href="/docs/stacktraces">Read more &raquo;</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</li>
		<li class="occurrences top-left">
			<div class="bubble">
				<p>
